    "3dc88749-f8c3-44c4-ba35-1422c56a3258": {
      "type": "simple",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "An ancient, clandestine brotherhood said to predate the earliest empires, the ",
              "textFormat": "description"
            },
            {
              "text": "{{Order_of_the_Umbral_Lotus}}",
              "variable": true,
              "textFormat": "description"
            },
            {
              "text": " safeguards forbidden knowledge and ancient rituals. Rumored to wield the power of shadow and petals, they manipulate court politics and whispers from the darkness, ensuring the balance of power remains hidden beneath layers of secrecy.",
              "textFormat": "description"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "parentId": "091fe407-27f9-4f2d-82cc-cfc3b5c7a2a4",
      "styles": {
        "paddingBottom": "8px"
      },
      "id": "3dc88749-f8c3-44c4-ba35-1422c56a3258"
    },
    "dcb7aa88-47f2-4580-b892-887238b9185f": {
      "type": "simple",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Basic Information",
              "textFormat": "underline-h2"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "parentId": "091fe407-27f9-4f2d-82cc-cfc3b5c7a2a4",
      "id": "dcb7aa88-47f2-4580-b892-887238b9185f"
    },
    "39b2aa8e-4313-4d08-abf3-25f2160c2faa": {
      "type": "simple",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Type: ",
              "textFormat": "paragraph",
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": "Secret Society",
              "textFormat": "paragraph"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Alignment: ",
              "textFormat": "paragraph",
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": "Lawful Neutral",
              "textFormat": "paragraph"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Influence: ",
              "textFormat": "paragraph",
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": "National. The Order’s agents sit in every major court and bureaucracy, steering policy through whispers, forged documents, and hidden threats. Even nobles unaware of its existence find their decisions shaped by invisible hands.",
              "textFormat": "paragraph"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Headquarters: ",
              "textFormat": "paragraph",
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": "The Jade Sanctum, a concealed labyrinth beneath the Imperial City’s Merchant Quarter shrine, accessible only through a hidden passage guarded by living ink seals.",
              "textFormat": "paragraph"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Methods: ",
              "textFormat": "paragraph",
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": "Operating through a network of spies and assassins, the Order uses coded correspondence, subterfuge, and ritual magic to bend events to their will. They employ blackmail, subtle enchantment, and the occasional discreet elimination of threats.",
              "textFormat": "paragraph"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Allies: ",
              "textFormat": "paragraph",
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": "Silver Scribes League, House Kage (clandestine cell)",
              "textFormat": "paragraph"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Rivals: ",
              "textFormat": "paragraph",
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": "Crimson Sun Assembly, Imperial Vanguard",
              "textFormat": "paragraph"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Weaknesses: ",
              "textFormat": "paragraph",
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": "Rigid adherence to ancient codes slows rapid response, Overreliance on secrecy makes them vulnerable to exposure, Fractures among council members over interpretation of the Old Rituals",
              "textFormat": "paragraph"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "parentId": "091fe407-27f9-4f2d-82cc-cfc3b5c7a2a4",
      "styles": {
        "paddingBottom": "8px"
      },
      "id": "39b2aa8e-4313-4d08-abf3-25f2160c2faa"
    },
